title: Four Piece Combo
description: Would you rather be Tom Brady’s child or Patrick Mahomes’ pitbull? The return of the mental health update (17:30). Why are people obsessed with their high school jersey number (29:50)? The Texans leaving teams on read (38:20). A brief discussion of “clout” and those who chase it (47:56). Is a rotary a roundabout or something more problematic (1:09:20)? Coach Prime had his stuff stolen, maybe, but probably not (1:30:05). Bathroom fights (1:40:00), Jenny/Jennifer (1:46:07), and dating someone with the same name as you (1:59:26).
